<h2 class="bold font-l">Nancy's past</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Nancy used to be a part of the Stingers, but she left them to spend time with her family. However, the Stingers took her departure as an act of betrayal and vowed revenge. </p>
</div>
